latestPosts.caption:
Sometimes it's the unexpected that turn out to be the best . My fashion choices have always been sartorial . As are  risks and opportunities which rule my life . @gauravguptaofficial has been making news globally dressing the best of celebrities worldwide . And when he offered to get one of his Paris show look down for me I was elated to say the least. It reached on time for the most important occasion . That of the title montage. It was surreal shooting in a Nitin Desai set . So 80s , with a dusty table and gigantic chandelier hanging over it in a hall , I passed by , while waiting for the next shot , which I jumped on and took these shots Impromptu. This outfit needed to be seen in its entirety ! For posterity ! 
What's next ? Back to reality till season 3 releases later in the year ! 
Fabulous Lives Vs Bollywood Wives , only on @netflix_in .
.
Outfit : @gauravguptaofficial .
Makeup : @savleenmanchanda.
Sapphire and diamond earrings ams ring @aloklodhajewels 
.
#fabulouslivesofbollywoodwivesseason3 #fabulouslives #netflix #dharmaproductions #gauravgupta #gauravguptacouture

Last night saw a myriad of personalities that have known Gudda through his life . His precious girl friends , some who wore their bridal  outfits which he painstakingly discussed to design and was there to dress them personally on the wedding day , his prodigies who worked and learnt everything they successfully do today under their own label , his favourite models who he embraced as family , his friends who he loved back with as much fervour , and his family who are still processing his loss.

I opened the show , walking into this gigantic space , enveloped with Photograoghs of Gudda and me , wearing an ensemble which is a staple in my wardrobe . I tried hard not to trip or cry . 
A few weeks ago there was a beautiful tribute that @bazaarindia had during their annual event which was special as his friends paid a tribute to someone who we all loved as  a friend and brother . 
Walking last night with some of our OG models , I wonder why magazines don’t have enough features with these absolute beauties often enough . A discussion to be had for sure .
Emotions ran high and I missed my cue for the final walk -through as I watched @sonamkapoor backstage with tears rolling down and all of us crying with her, missing the man , the legend , the king of good times laughter and dancing .. Gudda forever .
@rohitbalofficial #gudda @fdciofficial @bazaarindia .
Show Directors : @preferredprofessionals @aparnabahlbedi @anishabahl .
Styling : @nupurmehta18 .

On the eve of Republic Day , a Bengali from Calcutta transported us to my roots , within the confines of a very modern building in the heart of Bombay . Apart from his genius of creativity , Sabyasachi Mukherjee is deep rooted in his heritage and childhood coupled with his sharp business acumen which makes him today a globally recognised designer . Last night was an extravaganza India has not seen . With some of the most important international press and buyers , serving indian hospitality at its best only the way honestly I have seen in my Dior days , this was beyond spectacular . As a vociferous Bengali I felt proud to have witnessed this . We sat in blocks of seating named after Calcutta streets . Funnily enough mine was Middleton .. where my school is ! Loreto House ! I doubt that was a coincidence as the attention to detail was staggering ! Dom Perignon flowed and apparently twelve kilos of caviar consumed. Spoilt with the bar set very very high . Congratulations! 25 years of @sabyasachiofficial . A standing ovation well deserved ! So grateful to have been part of this .
Thank you @manav_angelo_kashyaphai @pareinathapar @hemali76 and the entire team of Sabyasachi .

latestPosts.caption:
Benares . The best choreographed show in the world is perhaps the Arati on the ghats of Varanasi. Sitting on a boat as you approach , the glistening Ganges , bells ringing at a distance , and the sight of the banks interspersed with  burning bodies on pyres. I float my wish on a leaf with a tea light and flowers , making a wish , watching it miraculously dodging the oars of the boats , out of sight . A city of Life , Death and Hope . The circle of life,  all a heady mix right in front of you . The magic and darkness and the centuries old history this city holds makes this one of the most fascinating destinations . Travelling with my friends and two of the world’s best creative designers was that much more of a treat making this an unforgettable experience . Thank you @taruntahiliani for making me part of this journey . One for the archives.
.
#benares #varanasi

latestPosts.caption:
Welcome back to #ANAFIED 

In conversation with me this time is serial entrepreneur @kalyanisaha 

Kalyani has worn many hats: a fashion accessories exporter, the Vice President of Dior in India, an art gallery owner #montagrarts , co-founder of Lulu & Sky and the founder of luxury silverware brand Rezon. 

Born in Kolkata, Kalyani was surrounded by fashion and the arts by her parents, both culture aficionados. After working across media, hospitality, and so on, her niche was luxury fashion, which she served as a trendsetter for when she pioneered the arrival of Dior in India.

Kalyani initially pursued her career in marketing and journalism whilst running four diverse vertical’s at @indianexpress .

Kalyani has ventured into the world of silverware, heading @rezonluxurysilverware ,another luxury brand that she founded.

The latest season of @fabulouslivesofbollywoodwives on @netflix_in has got everyone buzzing, especially with the addition of new faces like Kalyani Saha Chawla, who is already a household name in the Delhi high society.

Kalyani is also a very proud and doting mother to her wonderful daughter @tahira_tara with whom she shares with ex husband #VishalChawla 

do look out for the full episode in the coming days!
December 2024 - January 2025 . What a fabulous way to bring in the new year with my closest . ♥️ #goa #jaipur

Bye 2024! You were really good to me ! Ending it with my only consistent  source of joy in our favourite , Pink City .
Let Love continue to Rule in 2025 .
